# Steps to Run Project

1. `npm start` // starts the react js project
2. `cd server && npm run serve` // starts the nodejs server

# Installation

1. To install React dependencies run `npm install` in root directory
2. For node js dependencies first `cd` into `server` folder and then write `npm install`

- Must have Redis and Mongodb installed.
- Create account and then login. Once logged in, you will be asked to "Authorize" spotify account. You will be redirected to Spotify and will have to log in.
  Once done you will return to main window. This is where the work needs to be done, as currently it is simply retrieving music last played using Spotify API.
  We need a recommender system that will have actions users will take on a song after they have been retrieved from their spotify account.
